  "text": "The H3K14 me1 mark was reported to occur in both human and mouse [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , supporting the existence of the modification in cells. We have herein identified the first KMT capable of modifying this site in vitro. Further work will be required to validate the role of SET-D6 in the catalysis of H3K14 me1 in cells and the function of this mark.",
